---
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Adrian Lopez - Full-stack developer and AI enthusiast.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pt-32 pb-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <header class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        About <span class="gradient-text">Me</span>
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg text-surface-200">
        Hi, I'm <strong class="text-white">Adrian Lopez</strong> -- a full-stack developer and AI enthusiast
        passionate about building modern web experiences.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mt-8">What I Do</h2>
      <p class="text-surface-200">
        I specialize in building scalable web applications using cutting-edge technologies.
        From React and Astro on the frontend to Hono and Node.js on the backend, I love
        exploring what's possible with modern tools.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mt-8">This Blog</h2>
      <p class="text-surface-200">
        This site is my playground for experimenting with the latest web technologies.
        It's built as a monorepo with Turborepo, Astro 5, Hono, and features AI-powered
        chatbots, parallax animations, and examples in multiple frameworks.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mt-8">Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul class="text-surface-200 space-y-2">
        <li>Frontend: Astro 5, React 19, Tailwind CSS v4</li>
        <li>Backend: Hono, Drizzle ORM, Turso</li>
        <li>AI: Vercel AI SDK, LangChain.js</li>
        <li>Tooling: Turborepo, pnpm, Biome, Vitest</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
